風已經聚返軍心啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1e4f79d44094b8bdd5585932b1d960dbc7a322","tid":1634020,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802140817541e50fc67183488fae814d6ac652b2","tid":1634020,"uid":322498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"隨住政府刻意用反蒙面法為原本降降地溫既民情重新點火，國際戰線呢幾日既情況係好嚴峻。<br />\n衝衝仔女都真係要認真諗下係咪有d裝修做得太過牽強，例如燒銀行<br />\n呢度呢幾日都好多人傾裝修係咪要分黑藍紅分級制，就知道其實唔係人人接受到黑藍紅全部豪裝<br />\n<br />\n國際輿論開始轉風向，越黎越多篇幅講暴力示威(CNN: Violent protests)既破壞，連聯合國人權理事會高級專員Michelle Bachelet Jeria都話 &quot;we cannot accept people who use masks to provoke(挑釁) violence&quot;。 其中CNN用&quot;anti-government protesters&quot;反政府示威者黎形容反警暴求公義既示威者，BBC就用Rioters(暴徒)。問題係我地幾時有人話要推翻個政府？衝衝仔女又係咪一般外國搶劫果D暴徒？ 點解由鬼佬既角度睇會睇錯重點？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個原因就係你有太多太多太多搶眼球既事件比佢地報!</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n傳媒係一盤生意，係靠多讀者去賺多D錢，你越多D好撚靚既裝修畫面比佢登，佢就越多人睇!!!<br />\n你諗下，如果係報「反蒙面法」，佢張圖可以係D乜撚？唔同通登鄭若驊出黎？如果係報「用緊急法」，「司法覆核」又可以有咩吸引眼球既野？如果呢堆事同步發生，係一定只會登銀行黨鐵世紀豪裝同仆街的士佬遇獅鳥!<br />\n<br />\n和理非因為呢排勇武活動太多，太多人開始驚，依家d遊行連幾十萬人都冇。要時下刻記住民心係最大既抗爭力量，林鄭政府之所以咁多人反， 就係因為佢夾硬黎，不得民心。佢犯既錯係見風駛盡𢃇，以為技術上可以做就去做。勇武漸漸都開始一樣，有d人覺得點解唔做得xyz，我想講唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">技術</span>上唔做得，係<span style=\"color: red;\">策略</span>上唔做得，由近來多次冇足夠後排同和理非support令被捕前線急劇增加你就知道後排support係幾重要!  和理非靠既係數量，靠既係冇gear，打佢地係會引起人權人道問題，所以政府唔會太殘暴，人多狗亦唔夠膽猛攻。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢場運動要成功，係唔可以只靠衝衝仔女去犧牲，適時進退，養精蓄銳，時硬時軟同佢鬥長命先係上策。我地要盡力令國際輿論繼續focus講警狗係一班冇人性冇學識冇文化既社會敗類，政府係用呢班敗類黎打擊公義，侵犯人權，意圖謀殺! 咁樣和理非先可以再次<span style=\"color: red;\">百萬人上場</span>抗惡法，抵抗極權!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲有，以後裝緊修做賊偷野唔該即場獅鳥!!!! 到尋日公海仲有d濕9係度問點解可以裝修唔可以偷野! </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>BBC:</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=0fea7eb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>CNN:</strong><br />\n尋日：<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/06/asia/hong-kong-unrest-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-unrest-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b7008305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-unrest-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=5b9c6c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/06/asia/hong-kong-unrest-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\n前日：<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=bf107803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>UN Human rights chief :</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e615d1d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩手足要做野要揀時機，日後美國要過「香港人權及民主法」果排睇新聞，唔好經常搞到d國際輿論淨係講d示威者幾暴力，幾多野比人打爛! 到時有d咩變數我真係冇撚眼睇...<br />\n<br />\n香港人權及民主法呢兩條條文你一定要知同一定要支持！<br />\n凍結班虐待手足既仆街所有美國財產同禁入美國：<br />\nRequire the president to freeze U.S.-based assets of, and deny entry to the U.S. by, any individuals found responsible for abducting and torturing human rights activists in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n比被迫害手足走佬既後路，有比人拉過都可以有visa：<br />\nEstablish that U.S. visas won&rsquo;t be denied to applicants from Hong Kong on the basis of them having been arrested or detained while protesting for democracy or human rights."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c60c1d274b1e634c0243009923100e482f8eb41","tid":1634020,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3246bc6461f5b74e7774b3298d86e65720e14e4","tid":1634020,"uid":322498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:27:53.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b1c2ba292a338f8b1a2a9088ead64e006833c54","tid":1634020,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacb1dec822ef31a95784f19e801b6d2761d2d8d","tid":1634020,"uid":198958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a4278835bec791290ee756157db92a9260352ac","tid":1634020,"uid":322498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21588a96c1e27ca9a18563e28f70c3f3036e0cac","tid":1634020,"uid":198958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"我靜係見到裝修撚令藍鋪都要貼聲明變黃鋪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到美心同富臨有貼囉...<br />\n佢貼完改變唔到佢係藍心既事實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"所以要裝修"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"政府就喺想你裝 你估麻雀館有話事權?"},{"pid":"9d7aa4a4c3c6452533f92e4990da27bd9ca360ad","tid":1634020,"uid":322498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94a9cfdd4